\s Wakati Salama inapojaza roho
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Wakati \bd*\bd Salama \bd*\bd inapojaza roho, Na vile wakati wa taabu, Umenifundisha kusema kwa kweli\bd*\bd :\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Najua Mwokozi ni wangu.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\pc \bdit Ninajua Yesu Bwana, Ninapata \bdit*\bdit Salama \bdit*\bdit moyoni.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wakati Shetani anaponijaribu, Salama inachunga roho, Kwa maana Mwokozi ananikumbuka Na kunipa nguvu kushinda.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ninajua Yesu Bwana, Ninapata Salama moyoni.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Hukumu ya zambi sitaogopa tena, Mwokozi aliimaliza Saa alipobeba makosa \bd*\bd Kalvari\bd*\bd  Na kuyaondosha kabisa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ninajua Yesu Bwana, Ninapata Salama moyoni.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ninatazamia kurudi kwake Yesu Afike katika mawingu, Nione kwa macho ninayemupenda, Niishi milele na yeye.\bd*
